    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Leave it to Martha Stewart to create Halloween welcome mats so attractive you would be too scared to step on them. The coir doormats are available in witch or owl designs, $24 each, from www.marthabymail .com.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Leave it to Martha Stewart to create Halloween welcome mats so attractive you would be too scared to step on them. The coir doormats are available in witch or owl designs, $24 each, from www.marthabymail .com.</p>
        <p>A less expensive alternative is a jack-o'-lantern doormat, $10, at Old Navy. On Wednesday, it's back to AstroTurf and a daisy.</p>
        <p>PULSE</p>
      </block>
